# --- Benchmark output ------------------------------------------------------
# A reference snapshot of results/ IS tracked so every table and figure in the
# paper is backed by committed data; re-running the scripts overwrites these,
# and `git diff` then shows how your machine compares to the reference run.
# Only the transient smoke report is ignored.
results/isaaclab_smoke_report.txt

# --- Logs / scratch --------------------------------------------------------
*.log
tmp/
scratch/
*.ckpt
*.pt
*.pth
*.npz

# Keep an empty results/ around so the path exists for first-time users
!results/.gitkeep
